data.description: USDA approved meaning 0% down eligibility!! Welcome to this beautiful, new (Dec 2022), freshly painted throughtout hardly lived in home in the Sumter Villas community! You don't have to wait till February for new construction. 1746 Nebraska Loop is on a corner lot and backs up to conservation so no rear neighbors or an obstructed view. Plus, this Phase is complete therefore no construction noise. Stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and plenty of cabinet space are provided in the spacious kitchen. Gorgeous flooring throughout main living areas and all bedrooms have large walk-in closets. This home is close to I-75 and the Turnpike for a fast and easy commute. Home warranty is still in place till the end of the year. Come see this home today and make it your own!
